{
  "stem": "2316.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We stored wood in there, and products, and food, and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was like a big wooden garage in the back of our home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was long, narrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father decided with his cousin that they're going to build a wall there, a wooden wall.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In case the Nazi's come, we'll just go in the wall and hide, a secret wall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they built it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was done secretly at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then like they took away everybody's businesses and gold and jewelry, or whatever each one had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they used a man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took all the man away to work in the factories or whatever they delegated they did in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very small shtetl so transportation wasn't necessary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just taken to clean roads, to work in the-- they needed the leather goods for the army, I guess, for the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they, and we had leather goods factories, like small shops.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody had to work there, all the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If one was a peddler, if one was something else, everybody had to work in the leather factories.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that-- and they continued like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, of course, everything was very sparse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't have just, a little bit of whatever we had left in the gardens to live on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, and then they took everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They started take some men away from out of the shtetl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said they're taking them to work, in this town, and that town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the men started to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was hidden in that wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they came to us and they asked where my father, and my older brother, we said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's someplace in Stutt.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
